{"tid":1479277,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"逾350名行政主任再聯署　促政府回應市民五大訴求","createTime":"2019-08-16T23:42:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T23:48:14.000Z","uid":50457,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cf54af38a28fe454159400bc9579a523e66eea9a","tid":1479277,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T23:42:45.000Z","msg":"逾350名特區政府行政主任再度聯署公開信，促請當局必須正面回應廣大市民提出的五大訴求，尤其是正式撤回修訂逃犯條例及依從社會廣泛共識成立獨立調查委員會。<br />\n<br />\n公開信表示，若然政府繼續寸步不讓，對話空間必然壓縮怠盡，再次令公務員同事失望，不排除引致再次以集會、遊行、按章工作或參與罷工等方式忠誠直諫，以圖挽救香港於水火。<br />\n<br />\n公開信指出，近兩個月來，廣大市民已清楚表達訴求，期望特首可以虛心聆聽及回應。作為有良知的香港人及公僕，需要再次表達關注，又強調身為行政主任，在執行職務時絕對堅守政治中立的原則，致力服務市民。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1474951-20190816.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1474951-20190816.htm&d=u3dPEc69Okhs1BcqxCk75ZmLjsYRFZgpJr%2B2v3iO%2BBA%3D&h=c575b609\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1474951-20190816.htm&h=73509366\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1474951-20190816.htm</a>"},{"pid":"d512c851aefa14d8b5762ba1e22f3c00d7fa9e84","tid":1479277,"uid":113183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T23:43:51.000Z","msg":"多謝AO<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45d405c21eea9ebbff16f8ab56baeb4a3e746237","tid":1479277,"uid":64345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d512c851aefa14d8b5762ba1e22f3c00d7fa9e84","tid":1479277,"uid":113183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T23:43:51.000Z","msg":"多謝AO<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T23:44:53.000Z","msg":"EO黎喎"},{"pid":"f9cba51104539cdd92e4a1edfb2cf58231cc1618","tid":1479277,"uid":113183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45d405c21eea9ebbff16f8ab56baeb4a3e746237","tid":1479277,"uid":64345,"lik